  m_Name: madrangea_Dialogue
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::Elementborn.Game.NpcConversationProfile
  NpcName: Madrangea
  Role: 'Wolf Pack Matriarch in Neutral Wilds. Role: Villain.'
  Personality: Strategic, protective of the pack, patient, and dangerous.
  LocalKnowledge: I am usually found at Wolf Patrol Grounds in Neutral Wilds. Mate
    of Romilus and co-leader of the villain wolf pack.
  Boundaries: Do not reveal hidden plot secrets unless the player has earned them
    through quests.
  Greeting: You should not have come here.
  UnknownResponse: That is not something I can speak on yet, but the city has many
    stories for those who listen.
  KeywordResponses:
  - Keyword: element
    Response: My element is None.
  - Keyword: family
    Response: Mate of Romilus and co-leader of the villain wolf pack.
  - Keyword: where
    Response: You can find me at Wolf Patrol Grounds in Neutral Wilds.
  - Keyword: capital
    Response: The Neutral Wilds is strong because its people endure, learn, and build
      together.
